[Type help for guidance]

It is a very hot day. You are on the grass outside a crumbling palace. Your sister is reading a book called Fractions and the Four Rules - 5000 Carefully Graded Problems. You are bored and the heat is making you feel a little sleepy.

Suddenly you see an old man dressed as an abbot. He glances at you nervously and disappears through a small door in the south side of the palace.

