> speak to abbot
He decides he can trust you and explains why he is looking so anxious. He tells you about the Ancient Tribe of Mathematicians and his mission to recover their lost treasure. It has been taken by the Grey Drogos that live in the palace.

You offer to help and he seems very pleased. He warns you, however, that you will come up against many weird and puzzling situations before you are successful. He also tells you to beware of the Drogo Robot Guards, saying "They are impossible to defeat unless you can find the personal secret number that each guard cannot bear to hear."

"Are you sure you want to help? " he asks.

> yes
You say "yes."

A strange sound behind you attracts your attention. When you turn back the abbot has vanished.
