The spider says "I have something here which may help you, but the Drogos have made it invisible."

"Would you like me to help you find it?"

> yes
You say "yes."

"If I spin a special web that encloses this room the Drogos' magic will be defeated. You can see this room has four edges where the walls join, four edges where the walls meet the floor, and another four edges where the walls meet the ceiling. I must spin a silk thread that passes along each of these 12 edges twice--once in each direction. The thread must not be broken and, as I have only a limited supply, I must not go along any edge more than twice."

"The trouble is I am a rather old, short-sighted spider so you'll have to help me. So if you could tell me whether to turn left or right when I reach the end of each edge, I might just manage it. Say START when you want me to begin."
